subject: Empire State Building (NYC)
lead_paragraph: The defending champions won again in the 31st annual Empire State Building Run-Up. Thomas Dolt, 23, of Germany won the men’s elite race for the third consecutive year, covering the 1,576 steps from the lobby to the 86th floor observation deck in 10 minutes 8 seconds. Rickey Gates of Boulder, Colo., was second. Suzy Walsham, 34, of Australia repeated as the women’s champion in 12:44.
